## **Update all packages from storybook**

```bash
npx npm-check-updates '/storybook/' -u && npm install
```

## **Change port for create-react-app**

Change the start script to from

```
"start": "react-scripts start"
```

to

```
"start": "PORT=3006 react-scripts start"
```

[Source](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40714583/how-to-specify-a-port-to-run-a-create-react-app-based-project)

## **Close single simulator in Xcode**

Select Simulator.. Go into File Menu -> Close window or press [Command + W ]. It will close the simulator which is on top.[Source](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/45165635/how-to-quit-or-close-single-simulator-from-opened-multiple-simulator-in-xcode-9)

